1
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:11,880
Hurry.

2
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:25,720
Done.

3
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,560
Excellent.

4
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,640
Pack up your things quickly.

5
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,690
Those cunning Chinese.

6
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:40,520
It took so much effort.

7
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,259
It disappeared again.

8
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:46,890
Section Chief Qian.

9
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,900
Where is the highest point

10
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,120
on Xinshi Street?

11
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:53,520
The Chinese Eastern Railway Administration Building.

12
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,920
How high is the building?

13
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:55,680
Well,

14
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,280
probably, maybe...

15
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:58,840
It seems

16
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,800
the main building is three stories high,

17
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,040
and there's an observation deck on the top floor

18
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,640
overlooking the whole city.

19
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,440
Right.

20
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,680
Captain Matsuda.

21
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,560
I propose that

22
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,800
the Police Department, Security Bureau, and Electric Bureau

23
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,860
take joint action.

24
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,880
By combining power control, geographical segmentation,

25
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,560
and direction-finding technology,

26
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:16,079
we can systematically compress the survival space

27
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:18,680
of the underground Communist radio stations.

28
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,800
This will enable full control

29
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,240
from detection

30
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,360
to capture,

31
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:29,400
leaving the remaining underground Communist radio stations

32
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,329
nowhere to hide.

33
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:43,000
The combat environment is getting worse.

34
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,960
You and Auntie

35
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,090
must also protect yourselves.

36
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,079
Your auntie and I

37
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:51,300
have nothing left to long for.

38
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,840
Our son died in a labor camp.

39
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:57,370
His bones were buried in the outskirts north of the city.

40
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,880
That's a mass grave.

41
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,280
Our little grandson

42
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,890
was thrown to death by the Japs.

43
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:11,120
Our daughter-in-law

44
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:13,120
was forced by those animals

45
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,130
to jump into the Songhua River.

46
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:21,079
My wife couldn't take the shock

47
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,560
and went mute.

48
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,720
I told my wife,

49
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,880
the radio waves you send out

50
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,600
are our son's soul

51
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,280
speaking.

52
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:39,930
Brother.

53
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,040
That's how it is.

54
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,800
You have to help me discipline Lingzi.

55
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,160
She never listens to me.

56
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,760
Besides,

57
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,160
from what I heard,

58
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,480
Lingzi and Qin Na

59
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,690
seem to have an unusual relationship.

60
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,880
I'm just worried now

61
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:58,020
about Lingzi and the underground party.

62
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,760
You spoiled her, you know that?

63
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,640
Preaching about freedom of love all day long.

64
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,720
Freedom of love?

65
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,320
Where she goes and what she does,

66
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,520
you never dared to ask.

67
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,440
Now look at her.

68
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,800
Completely free.

69
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,279
From now on,

70
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:19,000
discipline Lingzi more and keep an eye on her.

71
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,800
What if something happens to her?

72
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,000
I know, Brother.

73
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:25,700
Anything else?

74
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,120
Brother.

75
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,240
Zhu Tianyou from the Tokko

76
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,240
was stabbed to death at home last night.

77
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,200
Did you hear about it?

78
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,280
I heard.

79
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,960
There have been several cases like this recently.

80
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:50,600
Brother, tell me.

81
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,640
Who did this?

82
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:57,240
This is something Qian Yugui should worry about.

83
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,440
Why are you asking me?

84
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,500
Brother, I'm leaving.

85
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,800
Take care on the road.

86
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,400
Okay.

87
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,170
Stop the car.

88
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:28,160
Miss Qin, you're back.

89
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:28,840
Uncle.

90
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:34,920
Sister Qin.

91
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,530
There's a man

92
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,960
looking for Vice President Lin.

93
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,220
He looked very fierce.

94
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,810
Looking for Lin Heming?

95
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,360
Didn't you tell him

96
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,760
he left the harmonica club?

97
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:44,480
I did.

98
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,200
He said if Vice President Lin isn't here,

99
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,520
looking for you is fine too.

100
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,520
Looking for me?

101
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,659
He's been waiting for a long time.

102
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,160
Brother Shen.

103
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:15,200
Brother Shen.

104
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,080
What brings you here so late?

105
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,200
Brother,

106
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:22,600
I have some private matters with your Teacher Qin.

107
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,920
You can go back to your business.

108
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,650
I won't let you hurt Sister Qin.

109
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,300
It's fine, Xiaoxiong.

110
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,320
Shen Ling's brother, Brother Shen.

111
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,440
Brother Shen,

112
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:31,960
I'm Gu Xiaoxiong,

113
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,330
Shen Ling's friend.

114
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:34,880
Okay.

115
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:36,340
I'll remember you.

116
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:38,080
Go do your work.

117
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,520
Brother Shen, what's wrong?

118
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,810
The windows of your harmonica club

119
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,760
are too clean.

120
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,680
What?

121
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,160
In Harbin,

122
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,560
there's a lot of wind, sand, and dust.

123
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,930
Every household's windows

124
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,760
are covered with a layer of dust.

125
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,210
But your harmonica club

126
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,360
is too clean.

127
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:18,560
And the people here can't tolerate any dirt either.

128
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,840
That's not very good.

129
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,840
Brother Shen, you really are experienced.

130
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:30,040
Thank you for the advice, Brother Shen.

131
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,930
Where is Lin Heming?

132
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,040
He's not with you?

133
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,800
Lin Heming is the president of Shunfa Advertising Agency.

134
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,060
He loves the harmonica

135
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:43,180
and invested some money here.

136
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:45,120
So I gave him a nominal position

137
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,360
in the harmonica club.

138
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,680
He rarely comes here.

139
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,850
You can come to me if you need anything.

140
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,120
Did he tell you

141
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,360
he lost something?

142
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:56,720
No.

143
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,700
All right then.

144
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,920
Tell Lin Heming

145
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,560
that if he wants

146
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,040
the thing he lost,

147
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,860
he can come to me for it.

148
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:12,920
Okay, no problem.

149
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:14,360
I'll pass on the message.

150
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,480
Teacher Qin,

151
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,640
if you don't want your harmonica club

152
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:21,320
and yourself to get into trouble,

153
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,440
don't tell me

154
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:25,340
that the thing has nothing to do with you.

155
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,250
What do you mean?

156
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,799
Boss Shen, take care.

157
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:38,970
Stop the car.

158
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,480
But I didn't expect

159
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,480
that thing

160
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,520
could get you killed.

161
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,160
Brother Shen.

162
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:09,420
Lingzi and I are good sisters.

163
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,080
We are not strangers.

164
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,960
So just speak your mind.

165
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,240
Good.

166
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,610
I like your straightforwardness.

167
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:17,970
Let's sit down and talk.

168
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,400
Tell me the truth.

169
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:27,120
Does Shen Ling

170
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,680
know what you and Lin Heming

171
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,760
have done?

172
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:40,800
I understand.

173
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:43,840
I came to ask you

174
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,340
if you can let Shen Ling

175
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,400
leave your society.

176
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:50,960
Brother Shen.

177
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,160
Lingzi is an adult.

178
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,080
What she wants to do or not do

179
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,240
is her own choice.

180
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,320
I am asking you.

181
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:59,720
Can you make a clean break with Shen Ling

182
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,760
and stop her from associating with the Harmonica Society?

183
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,620
You should ask Lingzi about this.

184
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,460
I was afraid my sister and I

185
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:08,760
would fight bitterly over your business,

186
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:09,840
so I came here.

187
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,480
If Lingzi agrees,

188
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,520
can you give the thing back to me?

189
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:17,640
If Lingzi is safe,

190
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,780
I will return it immediately.

191
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,260
What if Lingzi doesn't agree?

192
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,220
Section Chief, everyone is here.

193
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,720
Good job, San'er.

194
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:32,970
Take them up.

195
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,700
Take them away.

196
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:45,940
This must be Chen Yu's older brother, Boss Shen.

197
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,720
Yes.

198
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,400
Chen Yu has a

199
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,680
brother with connections in both worlds.

200
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,010
It is really a blessing.

201
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,960
Worthy of being the boss of the plainclothes squad.

202
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,600
You are quite familiar with the business.

203
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,800
It's what I should do.

204
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:03,200
Sister Qin, we can't listen to my brother on this.

205
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,860
I will go ask him for the radio.

206
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,000
But your brother's attitude is very firm.

207
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,160
What happened at your Harmonica Society

208
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,320
last night?

209
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:12,320
My second brother Chen Yu told me everything.

210
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,320
The reason he helped you so much

211
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,610
is because Shen Ling

212
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:16,860
is also his sister.

213
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:22,740
You should know what their relationship is.

214
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:29,520
If I see you with Shen Ling again,

215
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:33,240
don't blame me for turning hostile.

216
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,660
I have my ways to deal with you.

217
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:47,920
For your safety,

218
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:50,360
I feel he can do anything.

219
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:55,560
Lingzi.

220
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,160
Come sit here.

221
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:04,680
Lingzi.

222
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,160
I mean,

223
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:08,240
to send you to the Anti-Japanese United Army.

224
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:08,880
In this way.

225
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:10,480
No, I don't agree.

226
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,600
The combat environment is so harsh right now.

227
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,200
I'm not going anywhere at a time like this.

228
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:14,800
I want to stand with you,

229
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:17,660
together with the comrades, and fight side by side.

230
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,640
Lingzi.

231
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:21,800
I don't want you to leave either.

232
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:23,120
The work and environment here,

233
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,640
you are the most familiar with.

234
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,600
But what about your older brother?

235
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,600
I'll figure something out with my older brother.

236
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,160
My older brother loves me the most.

237
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:31,400
Although he's not my biological brother,

238
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:33,600
we are closer than biological brothers.

239
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:35,000
Everything I have today,

240
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,960
including my life,

241
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,980
was given by my older brother.

242
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,360
Zhuzi.

243
00:12:58,520 --> 00:12:59,680
Let me go.

244
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,210
Come, come. Put it here.

245
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:16,600
Help!
